{
  "texts": [
    "Another promising area of research focuses on the user experience, examining how individuals from various backgrounds interact with and are impacted by LLMs.",
    "The engagement with underrepresented communities in the design and testing phases of model development can ensure that AI technologies cater to a broader spectrum of needs and perspectives.",
    "Moreover, the study underscores the need for ongoing evaluation and refinement of fairness benchmarks, adapting them to reflect changing societal norms and technological advancements.",
    "Ultimately, the pursuit of bias-free LLMs requires a holistic approach, embracing the complexity of human language and culture, and committing to continuous improvement and ethical vigilance.",
    "This study performed on a comparative analysis of bias and fairness across three state-of-the-art Large Language Models (LLMs): ChatGPT-4, Google Gemini, and Llama 2, employing the Google BIG-Bench benchmark as a tool for evaluation."
  ]
}